==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Underlet
<hw>Un`der*let"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>To
let below the value.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>All my farms were <qex>underlet</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Smollett.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To let or lease at second hand; to sublet.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Underletter</ent>⟦br⟧
